imdb.plot outline: A British man who can use his motorpowered mouth to say sentences at breakneck speeds puts his speaking skills to good use: by creating a channel where he reviews games and attempts to do the dirty deed of deciding whether or not a game deserves to be "slaughtered" or "salvaged". Peppered with variety, charm, and humor that bounces all over the place, Caddicarus is the guy to look for; whether you want an entertaining review, a nostalgia trip, or just feel like having a good giggle.
imdb.title: Caddicarus
plot: James "_Caddicarus_ (qv)" Caddick shares his personal experiences with video games and movies and delivers his judgment on whether they should be slaughtered or salvaged.::jhansell-89168

A British man who can use his motorpowered mouth to say sentences at breakneck speeds puts his speaking skills to good use: by creating a channel where he reviews games and attempts to do the dirty deed of deciding whether or not a game deserves to be "slaughtered" or "salvaged". Peppered with variety, charm, and humor that bounces all over the place, _Caddicarus_ (qv) is the guy to look for; whether you want an entertaining review, a nostalgia trip, or just feel like having a good giggle.
